   The following Arizona Republic story has been added for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for Sunday, Jan. 9. If you have
any questions, please contact the Repub lic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
MCCAIN _ Sen. John McCain, hoping to defuse a potential political
bomb, opened his files Saturday and released letters he wrote to
U.S. regulatory agencies in behalf of large campaign donors. One of
the letters was written for a satellite firm McCain aided
